Media News Cc attached a copy of the Media News Confirmation They agree to everything but want to add one more condition If ENA closes on the KPM Lasara LP newsprint mill before the expiration date of the Swaption and all the other conditions in the current agreement are met then ENA must give Notice of Exercise to Counterparty I am not sure about all of the details of the KPM Lasara LP newsprint deal It is my understanding that Kafus is raising money to build the mill and we are helping them out If you have any questions about the project contact Joe Jure ext he is the deal maker on this Transaction or Dick Robinson ext he is working on the KPM Lasara project you can also talk to Bob Crane I will be out tomorrow so if you have any questions please leave me a voice mail or contact Gordon Heaney ext I will be back in the office on Friday Thank you Jarrod

Rand Whitney CollarI have attached draft Confirmation of a Collar with Rand Whitney They want to go live with this deal today and send out an executable Confirmation Tanya wants to put a provision in the confirmation that states that the deal is subject to Credit approval If we do not get credit approval Tanya will kill the deal I have left a message with Tanya asking her exactly what she wants to say in the Confirmation Please let me know what you think of the Collar the way it is writtne and if we have any language to use for the credit provision I have a meeting at an should be back at my desk by Thanks Jarrod PS SITA you were going to take a look at the governing law

Ekman Co Floor Cc attached a deal ticket for a transaction done today This deal was done with a Swedish counterparty I assume we need a deemed ISDA I told them not to expect the Confirmation until sometime on Wednesday Please call me if you have any questions Thank you Jarrod Forwarded by Jarrod CyprowHOUECT on PM Enron North America Corp From Jay Epstein PM To Tanya CT Jarrod CT John CT Paul NRON Gordon NRON Charlie CT cc Andrew R CT Bob CT Steve CT Subject Ekman Co Floor We have agreed to sell a oneyear floor to Ekman Co for ADMTmonth of NBSK PIX with a strike of US from November to October The deal was arranged through TFS and the ticket is attached Please let me know if there are any problems Thanks Jay

RE Clorox comments to the ISDA Master Agreement and Credit Support AnnexI will be out of the office tomorrow and Thursday Can we get together Friday morning to just review what you discuss Thanks Jarrod Original Message From Shackleton Sara Sent Monday October PM To Phillips Rebecca Cc Cyprow Jarrod Bailey Susan Rohauer Tanya Subject FW Clorox comments to the ISDA Master Agreement and Credit Support Annex Rebecca Per our conversation attached please find Cloroxs blackline You should have Aparnas file including the credit worksheet Also Aparna should have provided you wtih a copy of the ISDA boilerplate let me know if you need this or anything else The credit issues we should focus on include request for cross acceleration Part b page Cross Default amendment for operational issues Part b page Credit Event Upon Merger use of materially weaker definition Part c pages Additional Termination Events use of rating downgrade Part i pages Delivery of documents see page comments elimination of nonreliance representation pages elimination of affiliate setoff pages Change to definiton of Credit Support Amount Annex A page complete change to Threshold and Independent Amount Annex A pages Minimum Transfer Amount from to elimination of the MAC in Par to the Credit Support Annex Annex A page Enron Corp guaranty elimination of cap see Enron Corp guaranty I look forward to meeting with you on Wednesday Sara Shackleton Enron Wholesale Services Smith Street EBa Houston TX Ph Fax Original Message From Bailey Susan Sent Wednesday October PM To Shackleton Sara Cc Cyprow Jarrod Subject FW Clorox comments Sara Attached are Cloroxs comments to our ISDA draft provided to them in April Jarrod Cyprow would like to schedule a meeting with you on Monday afternoon October nd to discuss Cloroxs comments Let me know if I may be of assistance Susan Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday October PM To Bailey Susan Subject Re Clorox comments Susan Please let me know if
